channel.title: [PI] MTP V2 Client and or cache? 317
channel.description:
After 3 years and a new comp, I'm looking to get a client for my previous source used that marcbob created! It's called [b]MTP V2 Remake[/b]. I have the source, but do not have the normal client or the cache, only the webclient ready client w/o the cache. I can send that to anyone who wants it in return for the client for it (I believe it's called Fallen Pkers or Devotion Pk) - all the links I have checked on here are dead so, I'd appreciate some help!
So I need: -[b]Client that is for MTP V2 remake w same models[/b] -[b]MTP V2 cache for the webclient ready client[/b]
If anyone could help me out, I'd for sure appreciate it!
Thanks all
